      "author": "SharbelMarshi",
      "description": "## Fixes\r\n\r\n### TikZJax & LuaLaTeX (both engines)\r\n- Fix render crash **\"Offset is outside the bounds of the DataView\"** — broken SHA-256 padding in cache key hashing broke every render path\r\n\r\n### LuaLaTeX (desktop)\r\n- Fix **pdftocairo not found** when poppler is installed — `pdftocairo` rejects `--version`; probe with `-v` instead\r\n- Fix temp **working directory missing leading `/`** on macOS/iCloud vaults (`/Users/...` not `Users/...`)\r\n- Fix SVG export: pass correct output prefix to `pdftocairo -svg`\r\n- Use `window.require` for Electron spawn (Obsidian lint compatibility)\r\n\r\n### Obsidian community review\r\n- No static Node stdlib imports; temp file I/O via vault adapter\r\n- Dynamic `child_process` access for desktop LuaLaTeX only",
