      "author": "github-actions[bot]",
      "description": "Major editor and preview update since 1.3.5. Desktop keeps LuaLaTeX + TikZJax; **mobile is now supported** via bundled TikZJax.\r\n\r\n### Live preview & coordinate picking (desktop)\r\n\r\n- Floating inline live preview while editing inside a `tikz` block\r\n- Click the preview to insert `(x, y)` coordinates at the cursor\r\n- **Shift+click** snaps to horizontal or vertical from the last numeric coordinate in source\r\n- **`ccycle`** closes orthogonal shapes at 90° — type `ccycle` instead of `cycle` to snap the last corner and rewrite to `cycle`\r\n- Preview keeps the last good diagram visible while you edit incomplete paths\r\n- Pinned preview survives command palette / transient focus loss\r\n\r\n### Editor\r\n\r\n- Inline line numbers inside `tikz` blocks and `\\begin{tikzpicture}` (including empty lines)\r\n- Active-line highlight and matching `\\begin`/`\\end` pair highlight\r\n- Structural lint: unmatched envs/braces, unclosed `[` options, empty option keys, missing `\\usetikzlibrary`, PGFPlots `compat` hint\r\n- Auto-insert blank `tikzpicture` when opening a new ` ```tikz ` fence\r\n- Semicolon reminder on unfinished `\\draw`/`\\path` lines (off / hint / auto-append)\r\n- Auto-close `{`, `[`, `(`, `$` with smart Backspace\r\n- Auto `;` when starting a bare `\\draw` line\r\n\r\n### Autocomplete & snippets\r\n\r\n- Expanded snippet catalog: shapes, text, gates, wires, circuits, plots, coordinates\r\n- Named-node anchors (`node.north east`, etc.) and `\\LogicWire` node completion\r\n- Relative coordinate snippets (midpoint, `-|`, `++`)\r\n- `% align=` and `% grid=` directive completions\r\n- Context-aware suggestions inside `\\begin{axis}` and empty blocks\r\n\r\n### Commands\r\n\r\n- Open helper reference (searchable cheat sheet)\r\n- Insert TikZ template… (blank picture, flowchart, axis, logic circuit)\r\n- Format TikZ block\r\n- Wrap selection in `\\node{}` or `$...$`\r\n- Insert plot from function… (PGFPlots wizard)\r\n- What can I use here? (category snippet picker)\r\n\r\n### Rendering & appearance\r\n\r\n- **Mobile (iOS/Android):** TikZJax rendering in reading view; no local TeX required\r\n- Dark mode styles: auto-invert, brightness boost, or none; diagrams refresh on theme change\r\n- `% align=left/center/right` for block alignment in reading view\r\n- `% grid=N` injects an N cm background grid (stripped before render)\r\n\r\n### Errors & diagnostics\r\n\r\n- LaTeX log lines mapped back to note/editor lines\r\n- In-editor error highlight with column range\r\n- **Go to line** on error cards in reading view\r\n- **Fix** popup for one-click repairs (missing `;`, braces, typos, empty options)\r\n- Pre-render validation for empty option values\r\n\r\n### Helpers\r\n\r\n- New macros: `\\TextRTL`, `\\ResistorRow`\r\n- Existing helpers unchanged: `\\Circle`, `\\Arrow`, `\\Rect`, logic gates, wires, circuit symbols\r\n\r\n### Settings (new)\r\n\r\n- Starter block on new fence\r\n- Structural lint\r\n- Semicolon reminder\r\n- Auto-close brackets\r\n- Dark mode handling\r\n",
